title: Episode 237: Cum to Your Senses (Feat. King Von)
itunes:title: Episode 237: Cum to Your Senses (Feat. King Von)
description:
Rapper, King Von joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and opens up about his relationship with rapper, Asian Da Brat, his time in prison + encounters with the correctional officers, and much more. Make sure to check out his new album "Levon James." Enjoy!
